SELECT `n`.`iNotificationId` AS `notification_id`,`n`.`dtAddedAt` AS `notification_date`,`n`.`eNotificationType` AS `notification_type`,`n`.`vNotificationMessage` AS `message`,`u`.`iUserId` AS `notification_user_id`,concat(u.vFirstName,' ',u.vLastName) AS user_name,('') AS connection_type_by_logged_user,('') AS connection_type_by_receiver_user,`u`.`vProfileImage` AS `user_image` FROM `notification` AS `n` LEFT JOIN `users` AS `u` ON `n`.`iUserId` = `u`.`iUserId` WHERE `n`.`iNotifierId` = '10' AND `u`.`eStatus` = 'Active' ORDER BY `n`.`dtAddedAt` DESC
